  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A Phase 3, randomized, double-masked, vehicle-controlled trial to evaluate the safety and
      efficacy of ADX-102 ophthalmic solution in Subjects with non-infectious anterior-uveitis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
